think you're crazy.

1:13:05.059 --> 1:13:06.602
You're probably
right about that.

1:13:08.187 --> 1:13:09.480
I just don't give a damn.

1:13:21.367 --> 1:13:22.243
Hello?

1:13:24.454 --> 1:13:26.039
What are you talking about?

1:13:31.543 --> 1:13:33.046
